_sText: This map is a at dusk, so it is lowly lit. This is a beta version and I have put about 20 hours of creating and testing the map. There are still a few bugs in this version, but I've worked most of them out. In the next version of the map I release I will have some inatimate objects such as chairs, and lamps. I would love some suggestions on the map, and I hope you enjoy it!
